name: Banana Start Art
description: My contribution to the event #HENthousand - Traditional art, Second reinterpretation of the work of Maurizio Cattelan, creating a traditional art in my current style, painting with acrylic paint and namkin on paper mache banana on wooden canvas.  Dimensions: 33x27cm - Year: 2019 - Art By iagoDS - tt @iagods_ / ig @iagods_artes - Segunda releitura da obra de Maurizio Cattelan, criando uma arte tradicional no meu estilo atual, pintura com tinta acrílica e namquim sobre banana de papel mache em tela de madeira.  Dimensões: 33x27cm - Ano: 2019 - Art By iagoDS
